### League, Division, and Teams Tests

### 1. Leagues ReadList (Legacy) - Get user's leagues
POST {{baseUrl}}/eff/eff_api/Leagues.php?f=ReadList
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

_format=json&_type=byUserID&userID={{testUserID}}

### 2. Leagues ReadList (REST)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/leagues/readlist
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userID": {{testUserID}}
}

### 3. Divisions ReadList (Legacy) - Get divisions in a league
POST {{baseUrl}}/eff/eff_api/Divisions.php?f=ReadList
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

_format=json&_type=byLeagueID&leagueID={{testLeagueID}}

### 4. Divisions ReadList (REST)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/divisions/readlist
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "leagueID": {{testLeagueID}}
}

### 5. Teams ReadList (Legacy) - Get teams in a division
POST {{baseUrl}}/eff/eff_api/Teams.php?f=ReadList
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

_format=json&_type=byDivisionID&divisionID={{testDivisionID}}

### 6. Teams ReadList (Legacy) - Get teams in a league
POST {{baseUrl}}/eff/eff_api/Teams.php?f=ReadList
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

_format=json&_type=byLeagueID&leagueID={{testLeagueID}}

### 7. Teams ReadList (REST) - By Division
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/teams/readlist
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "divisionID": {{testDivisionID}}
}

### 8. Teams ReadList (REST) - By League
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/teams/readlist
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "leagueID": {{testLeagueID}}
}

### 9. DivisionNotes ReadList (Legacy) - Get notes for a division
POST {{baseUrl}}/eff/eff_api/DivisionNotes.php?f=ReadList
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

_format=json&_type=byDivisionID&divisionID={{testDivisionID}}

### 10. DivisionNotes ReadList (REST)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/division-notes/readlist
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "divisionID": {{testDivisionID}}
}
